\c 9
\s Ukubulawa kwabalecala
\p
\v 1 Wasememeza ezindlebeni zami \add nge\add*lizwi elikhulu esithi: Yenza ababonisi bomuzi basondele\x + 44.11.\x*, ngitsho wonke umuntu \add ele\add*sikhali sakhe sokuchitha esandleni sakhe.
\v 2 Khangela-ke, amadoda ayisithupha eza evela ngendlela yesango eliphezulu elikhangele ngasenyakatho\x + Jer. 49.8.\x*; njalo wonke umuntu \add ele\add*sikhali sakhe sokuphahlaza esandleni sakhe; njalo umuntu oyedwa phakathi kwawo\x + 10.2,6,7. Dan. 10.5. 12.6,7. Levi 16.4. Isam. 15.6.\x* wayegqoke ilembu elicolekileyo\x + 9.3,11.\x*, elophondo lweyinki\x + 9.3,11.\x* lombhali ngasokhalweni lwakhe; asengena, ema duze kwelathi lethusi\x + 8.5. Eks. 27.2.\x*.
\v 3 Lenkazimulo kaNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli yenyuka isuka ngaphezu \w kwekherubhi\w** eyayiphezu kwalo, yaya embundwini wendlu\x + 10.4,18. 46.2. 47.1.\x*; wasememeza umuntu\x + 10.2,6,7. Dan. 10.5. 12.6,7. Levi 16.4. Isam. 15.6.\x* owayegqoke ilembu elicolekileyo\x + 9.3,11.\x* owayelophondo lweyinki lombhali okhalweni lwakhe.
\v 4 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuye: Dabula phakathi komuzi, phakathi kweJerusalema, ufake uphawu emabunzini abantu\x + 3.8,9.\x* ababubulayo labakhalayo\x + Hlab. 119.53,136,158. 2 Pet. 2.8.\x* ngenxa yazo zonke izinengiso ezenziwa phakathi kwawo.
\p
\v 5 Lakwabanye yathi endlebeni yami\x + 9.2.\x*: Dabulani phakathi komuzi emva kwakhe, litshaye, ilihlo lenu lingahawukeli\x + 9.10. 5.11.\x*, njalo lingayekeli.
\v 6 Bulalani\x + 2 Lan. 36.17.\x* ngokuchitha abadala, abatsha, lezintombi, labantwana abancinyane, labesifazana; kodwa lingasondeli lakuwuphi umuntu\x + Isam. 9.4.\x* okulophawu\x + 9.6. Jobe 31.35.\x* phezu kwakhe, liqalise endaweni yami engcwele\x + Jer. 25.29.\x*. Basebeqalisa emadodeni amadala\x + 8.11,12,16. 8.1.\x* ayephambi kwendlu.
\v 7 Yasisithi kubo: Ngcolisani indlu\x + 7.21.\x*, ligcwalise amaguma ngababuleweyo. Phumani. Basebephuma, babulala emzini.
\p
\v 8 Kwasekusithi besababulala, mina-ke ngasala, ngathi\x + 11.13.\x* mbo ngobuso bami\x + Nani 14.5. 16.4,22,45. 20.6. Josh. 7.6.\x*, ngakhala ngathi: Hawu, Nkosi Jehova!\x + 4.14.\x* Uzachitha yini yonke insali yakoIsrayeli\x + 11.13.\x* ekuthululeni kwakho intukuthelo yakho phezu kweJerusalema?\x + 7.8.\x*
\v 9 Khona yathi kimi: Ububi bendlu yakoIsrayeli loJuda bukhulu kakhulukazi, lelizwe\x + 7.23. 8.17.\x* ligcwele amacala egazi, lomuzi ugcwele ukuphambuka, ngoba bathi: IN\nd kosi\nd* ilidelile ilizwe\x + 8.12.\x*, njalo iN\nd kosi\nd* kayiboni\x + 9.9.\x*.
\v 10 Lami-ke ilihlo lami kaliyikuhawukela\x + 9.9.\x*\x + 9.10. 5.11.\x*, njalo kangiyikuyekela; ngizakwehlisela indlela yabo ekhanda labo.
\v 11 Khangela-ke, lowomuntu owayegqoke ilembu elicolekileyo\x + 10.2,6,7. Dan. 10.5. 12.6,7. Levi 16.4. Isam. 15.6.\x*\x + 9.3,11.\x*, owayelophondo lweyinki okhalweni lwakhe, wabuyisela ilizwi esithi: Ngenzile njengoba ungilayile.